\begin_layout Standard
A large number of studies have been done on Stirling engine analysis.
 To describe a Stirling engine's behavior precisely is a difficult task
 due to the various losses and irreversibilities in the engine.
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Researchers have done a lot of work to build a precise Stirling engine model.
 Different models of Stirling engines were developed using empirical~
