 analytical~
\backslash
cite{Ohtomo1995,Rogdakis2004,Kongtragool2006,Puech2011,Formosa2010,Shazly2014,Cu
llen2011,Ahmadi2013,Ahmadi2013b,Tursunbaev2007} and numerical methods~
